G

GeneralInfoCalculator - Class in main.net.atos.uk.TravelDashboard.Dashboard.Main
This class is used to generate analysis data and charts for the main Dashboard: the labels showing total cost, who cost the most, in which location cost the most, etc., the line chart of total/last year, the bar chart of element/location/member.
GeneralInfoCalculator(ArrayList<Receipt>, String) - Constructor for class main.net.atos.uk.TravelDashboard.Dashboard.Main.GeneralInfoCalculator
The constructor will do all the calculation: several maps used to calculate value of amounts, line charts and bar charts.
generatePDF() - Method in class main.net.atos.uk.TravelDashboard.Dashboard.Report.PDFGenerator
